-- Yahoo declines comment on reports of Microsoft talks
-- 
-- Fri May 4, 2007 10:19am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/05/04/us-yahoo-microsoft-comment-idUSWEN772220070504

 

 BOSTON  (Reuters) - A Yahoo Inc. spokeswoman declined to comment on Friday on newspaper reports that her company is in talks with Microsoft Corp. about a possible merger or some kind of link-up between the two companies. 

 "We do not discuss rumors or speculation," Yahoo spokeswoman Joanna Stevens told Reuters.